    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那个不安的夏夜，湖的方向传来诡谲笑声。一次踏出帐篷的不慎之举，竟让你被拖入一片阴郁的流沼之地。这里遍布诡异的生物，埋藏着不为人知的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025310/extras/77919bb9c2cfe4fda6c631bec5a7f4d5.poster.avif?t=1760018500\" width=796 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025310/extras/77919bb9c2cfe4fda6c631bec5a7f4d5.webm?t=1760018500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025310/extras/77919bb9c2cfe4fda6c631bec5a7f4d5.mp4?t=1760018500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不久之后，会说话的猫就劝你潜入那座耸立在沼泽上的阴森城堡，而姜饼屋的女巫正在教你学习基础的炼药术。你是否有足够的勇气揭开这个地方的秘密？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025310/extras/2af17230ce157c619f6363aa3f94488e.webp?t=1760018500\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样化的谜题、炼药玩法与探索体验；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阴冷幽深的沼泽，暗藏致命谜团；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诡奇离异的居民，等待与你邂逅；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘质感的独特美术风格。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025310/extras/d6511e4d2ddaa51a59d352d4573facac.poster.avif?t=1760018500\" width=800 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025310/extras/d6511e4d2ddaa51a59d352d4573facac.webm?t=1760018500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025310/extras/d6511e4d2ddaa51a59d352d4573facac.mp4?t=1760018500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
